          "source_html": "<div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Questions 27 – 32</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Choose <strong>YES </strong>if the statement agrees with the claims of the writer, choose <strong>NO </strong>if the statement contradicts the claims of the writer, or choose <strong>NOT GIVEN </strong>if it is impossible to say what the writer thinks about this.</p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">27</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>The writer changed her mind about spending time in Tasmania.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_27\" id=\"opt_27_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q27\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_27_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. YES</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">27</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">YES</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">changed her mind<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体;\">，</span>Tasmania</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>As an eighteen-year-old living in the small Australian island state of Tasmania, moving to the ‘mainland’ could not happen soon enough. Now, ten years later, I look forward to going home.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到作者现在期待着回家，这与她十几岁的时候不同。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">28</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Andrew Bain believes that the effect MONA had on Hobart was immediate.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_28\" id=\"opt_28_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q28\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_28_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_28\" id=\"opt_28_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q28\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_28_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_28\" id=\"opt_28_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q28\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_28_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. YES</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">28</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">YES</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Andrew Bain<span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, </span>MONA<span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, </span>Hobart</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">B段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>Andrew Bain of The Sydney Morning Herald wrote, ‘In a virtual blink, Hobart’s cultural landscape has been transformed, with art, wine, fine food and stylish accommodation becoming integral features of the city... . If Hobart’s makeover has an origin, it’s the opening of MONA–the Museum of Old and New Art.’<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文中Andrew Bain说，MONA发挥了重要作用，使霍巴特的文化场景瞬间发生了变化。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同义替换：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In a virtual blink=immediate</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">29</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Other factors have contributed as much as MONA to Hobart</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>’</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>s transformation.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_29\" id=\"opt_29_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q29\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_29_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_29\" id=\"opt_29_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q29\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_29_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_29\" id=\"opt_29_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q29\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_29_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. NO</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">29</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">NO</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Other factors，MONA</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">B段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>MONA is said to have been solely instrumental in the reinvention of Hobart as a cultural hub.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到在霍巴特重新成为文化中心的过程中，MONA发挥了唯一的作用。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">30</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>The Tourism Industry Council of Tasmania works closely with the director of MONA.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_30\" id=\"opt_30_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q30\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_30_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_30\" id=\"opt_30_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q30\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_30_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_30\" id=\"opt_30_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q30\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_30_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> C. NOT GIVEN</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">NOT GIVEN</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文并未提到双方机构合作的紧密程度。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">31</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Many local residents are writing to The Mercury expressing concern about tourists</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><strong>’</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> length of stay in Hobart.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_31\" id=\"opt_31_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q31\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_31_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_31\" id=\"opt_31_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q31\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_31_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_31\" id=\"opt_31_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q31\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_31_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> C. NOT GIVEN</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">31</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">NOT GIVEN</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文并未提到居民写信传达担忧。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">32</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Tourists now regard MONA as a starting point for longer trips in Tasmania.</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> YES</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> NO</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_32\" id=\"opt_32_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q32\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_32_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> NOT GIVEN</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. NO</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">32</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">NO</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">starting point，longer trips</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">C段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>Rather than spending a week in the state and hiring a car to experience the beauty of the Tasmanian landscape, people are making short stays in Hobart only to visit the gallery.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到游客只是为了参观MONA而短暂停留，与将其视为起点相反。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Questions 33 – 37</strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Choose the correct answer.</p></div>\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">33</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Luke Martin plans to promote tourism in Tasmania by</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> focusing more on MONA as the leading attraction. </label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> combining trips to MONA with visits to other galleries.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> encouraging visitors to do activities that are not connected with art galleries.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_33\" id=\"opt_33_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q33\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_33_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> improving the quality of promotional information about Tasmania’s galleries.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. combining trips to MONA with visits to other galleries.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">33</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">B</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体;\">Luke Martin</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">D段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>According to Martin, possibilities for packaging up MONA with visits to other galleries around Tasmania are being investigated.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">卢克·马丁正在调查将参观摩纳与参观其他画廊结合起来的可行性，说明卢克·马丁计划将参观摩纳与参观其他画廊结合起来以促进旅游。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">34</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>According to the writer, what is especially interesting about MONA?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> the man who founded the gallery\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> its location close to a river</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> visitors’ responses to the gallery spaces </label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_34\" id=\"opt_34_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q34\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_34_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> the striking architecture of the building</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A. the man who founded the gallery\r\n</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">34</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">A</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">interesting about MONA</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">E段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span>MONA’s ‘wow factor’ comes from the notoriety of David Walsh, the museum’s millionaire founder, and his choice of unusual artworks.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到创始人David Walsh是画廊最让人惊奇的地方。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">35</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Why do visitors spend a long time at the gallery?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_35\" id=\"opt_35_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q35\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_35_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> There is a great number of exhibits.\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_35\" id=\"opt_35_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q35\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_35_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> Visitors tend to come in family groups.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_35\" id=\"opt_35_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q35\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_35_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> Many of the works are difficult to understand.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_35\" id=\"opt_35_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q35\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_35_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> The gallery has a physical effect on visitors.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> D. The gallery has a physical effect on visitors.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">35</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">D</span></p><p>定位关键词：</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">a long time，gallery</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">F段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">...</span>the urge to linger is a common feeling here. This is because the gallery engages all of the senses, and visitors often pause to experience the effect each artwork has on them.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到画廊吸引了所有的感官，使游客停下来体验艺术品。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">36</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>What does the writer say about the visitors to MONA?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_36\" id=\"opt_36_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q36\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_36_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> Older people spend longer there than younger people do.\r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_36\" id=\"opt_36_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q36\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_36_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> A wide variety of people are interested in MONA.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_36\" id=\"opt_36_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q36\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_36_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> The majority of visitors are young people.</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_36\" id=\"opt_36_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q36\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_36_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> The visitors are representative of gallery enthusiasts generally.</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> B. A wide variety of people are interested in MONA.</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">36</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">B</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">the visitors to MONA</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">F段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">People from all kinds of socioeconomic backgrounds are curious about what lies within the subterranean maze of MONA.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文提到不同社会经济背景的人都对MONA感到好奇。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同义词替换：</span></p><p>are curious about=are interest in</p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\">\r\n            <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                    <span class=\"q-num\">37</span>\r\n                    <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Why does the writer mention the coins at MONA?</strong></span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"opt-list\" style=\"margin:10px 0 10px 25px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_37\" id=\"opt_37_A\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\" value=\"A\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_37_A\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>A.</strong> to illustrate how interesting they are to visitors of modern galleries \r\n</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_37\" id=\"opt_37_B\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\" value=\"B\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_37_B\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>B.</strong> to explain why they are displayed in a separate section of the gallery </label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_37\" id=\"opt_37_C\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\" value=\"C\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_37_C\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>C.</strong> to argue that Walsh's collection is among the best in the world</label>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"radio_37\" id=\"opt_37_D\" data-zyz-question=\"q37\" value=\"D\">\r\n            <label for=\"opt_37_D\" style=\"cursor:pointer;\"><strong>D.</strong> to express admiration for the way that the exhibits are presented</label>\r\n        </div></div>\r\n                <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                    <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> D. to express admiration for the way that the exhibits are presented</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"analysis\"><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Q</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">37</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">D</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">定位关键词：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">the coins</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">原文：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">G段</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">, “</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">For me, one of the intriguing outcomes of this strategy was an intensified feeling that the makers of the coins and antiquities were the great contemporary artists of their time.</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">”</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"> </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">解析：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(31, 31, 31); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原文中作者感受到古代文物在现代作品中的展示中带来的强烈呈现效果。</span></p></div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div><div class=\"big-section\"><div class=\"group-instruction\"><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Questions 38 – 40 </strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Complete the summary using the list of words. Choose the correct word in each gap.</p></div>\r\n    <div class=\"word-bank-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"wb-title\">Options (Word Bank):</div>\r\n        <div class=\"wb-grid\">\r\n            <div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>A.</strong> challenge</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>B.</strong> pipe</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>C.</strong> visual</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>D.</strong> contribution</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>E.</strong> lasting</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>F.</strong> essential</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>G.</strong> ambition</div><div class=\"wb-item\"><strong>H.</strong> attraction</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n                    <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                        <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                            <span class=\"q-num\">38</span>\r\n                            <div class=\"q-text\"><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>The Bilbao effect</strong></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center; line-height: 1;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5;\">MONA has huge appeal for visitors to Hobart, just as Gehry<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">’</span>s Guggenheim Museum has for Bilbao. While MONA may lack the <span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q38\"></span> effect of the Guggenheim, David Walsh explains that MONA<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">’</span>s architect had a different objective when designing&nbsp;</p></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                        <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                            <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> C</div>\r\n                            <div class=\"analysis\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>Guggenheim</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>H段, “However, the architectural ‘wow factor’ of the Guggenheim was the most famous component of that city’s transformation, whereas Fender Katsalidis’s MONA does not have the same spectacular impact as the shimmering metal surfaces of Gehry’s building.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到Guggenheim以其视觉冲击力而闻名，而这是MONA没有的。</p></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                        <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                            <span class=\"q-num\">39</span>\r\n                            <div class=\"q-text\"><p><span style=\"text-wrap: wrap;\">MONA: unlike the architectural showcasing of the Guggenheim, with MONA there was a major <span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q39\"></span> that needed to be dealt with; the gallery was set beneath the ground.&nbsp;</span></p></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                        <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                            <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> A</div>\r\n                            <div class=\"analysis\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>set beneath the ground</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>H段, “Walsh himself abhors descriptions of MONA as the Bilbao of the south, saying that Fender Katsalidis solved a problem when he designed MONA, in executing a project of this scale in an underground location.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到沃尔什谈到了在地下设计MONA的挑战。</p><p><br/></p><p>同义替换：</p><p>set beneath the ground=underground location</p></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"q-block normal-q\">\r\n                        <div class=\"q-stem\">\r\n                            <span class=\"q-num\">40</span>\r\n                            <div class=\"q-text\"><p>In any case, both galleries have transformed their cities, just as successful public buildings have for thousands of years. It remains to be seen how the <span class=\"input-blank\" data-question=\"q40\"></span> of David Walsh will be expanded upon in Tasmania.</p></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <button class=\"btn-toggle\">显示解析</button>\r\n                        <div class=\"ans-box\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n                            <div class=\"ans-row\"><strong>正确答案：</strong> D</div>\r\n                            <div class=\"analysis\"><p>定位关键词：</p><p>David Walsh</p><p><br/></p><p>原文：</p><p>H段, “ Now the question is how Tasmania will build on David Walsh’s input into its cultural setting.”</p><p><br/></p><p>解析：</p><p>原文提到现在的问题是Tasmania 将如何在Walsh的贡献基础上再接再厉。</p></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    </div>",
